content_vision: I sip my morning coffee while watching the sunrise. I am in my own garden on the porch of my house. I admire the apple trees slowly swaying in the wind and the moving shadows. I enjoy the cool breeze on my face. I let the wind caress my hair. I listen to my instincts and already know my direction. No more fear.
structure_suggestion_description: Normal folk song about morning coffee
text:
Verse 1:
As the sun rises, I feel alive,
let the world keep talking, we'll keep thriving and thrive.
And with you by my side, I have no fear,
we'll face every challenge, hand in hand, my dear.
With the world spinning around us, we'll stand still,
letting love guide us, and we'll have our fill.
With each sip of my coffee, I feel my heart ignite,
your love is the fuel that keeps my flame burning bright.

Pre-Chorus 1:
Embracing this moment, with the future uncertain, but I know with you by my side,
our love will surpass any curtain.

Chorus 1:
We'll dance in the garden, hand in hand, as the sun rises high,
our love takes flight, with no fears, just you and I.
Together we'll rise, with love as our guide,
we'll conquer the world, side by side.

Verse 2:
With the world at our feet, we'll conquer all our fears,
let our love be the compass that guides us through the years.
Together we'll bloom, like the flowers in our garden,
our love will continue to grow, never burdened.
You are my compass, my guiding light,
through every storm, our love will never take flight.
Our love grows stronger with each passing day,
never faltering in any way.

Pre-Chorus 2:
Our love is a garden, constantly growing and evolving,
as we face every obstacle together.

Chorus 2:
Our love's light shines so bright, it's impossible to ignore,
we'll keep soaring higher, our souls forever intertwined.
Our love's journey is a glorious ride,
each moment together, we'll forever cherish and abide.

Chorus 3:
Our love's journey is a beautiful ride,
each moment together, we'll forever cherish side by side.
With every step forward, we leave the doubts behind,
our love's journey is filled with memories we'll forever hold in mind.

Bridge:
As the sun sets, we'll dance in the moon's embrace,
our love will shine brighter, with every step we take.
As we sway to the rhythm of our love,
the moon lights our path, shining from above.

Outro:
As I close my eyes and take a deep breath, I know our love will never falter,
even in the face of death.
